channel.title: Help, i tryed to add flames
channel.description:
Yo i tryed adding flames to my client following this tut http://silabsoft.org/smf/index.php?showtopic=12648&st=0&p=58002&hl=GUI%20interface&fromsearch=1&#entry58002
I get these errors, just two
[code]client.java:2311: cannot find symbol symbol : variable aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1_966 location: class client aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1_966 = new Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(aClass44_1053, "titlebox", 0); ^ client.java:2314: cannot find symbol symbol : variable aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1_967 location: class client aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1_967 = new Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub1(aClass44_1053, "titlebutton", 0); ^ Note: Some input files use or override a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Help greatly appreciated!
